{"tid":220304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗食評 - 閪記","createTime":"2017-04-28T00:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T01:12:14.000Z","uid":74981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdecacc0ecc4aeb601bdb6af44d7073105adefeb","tid":220304,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/52d96ec5c5704a15295fe6c5b99ed02e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F52d96ec5c5704a15295fe6c5b99ed02e.jpg&h=46ac2f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/501d912a681cdc7ed4e723c22bd29119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F501d912a681cdc7ed4e723c22bd29119.jpg&h=18aae39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一直想食哩間好耐，不過真係驚店如其名所以唔敢試。話說尋日經過太子又見到佢，又餓，廢事周圍行，入左去食。叫左豬紅粥，油炸鬼同鮮牛肉腸。<br />\n<br />\n豬紅粥: 18蚊唔貴，但好細碗。粥係好撚common果種hea底貨色，米極少，無米香，溝粉煮。而豬紅極難食，無味道，一質感差，一咬就散，係差唔多最劣等既貨色。<br />\n<br />\n油炸鬼: 擺到凍撚哂，不過唔會咬到齒唔開 (有d真係會係咁)，浸少少熱粥食，即刻變得鬆脆可口，係哩餐食得最滿意既。不過9蚊貴左d。<br />\n<br />\n鮮牛肉腸: 20蚊，唔算平。睇相都知好撚細條，質感差，太厚，唔滑都算，味道又差，有浸生粉味定唔知咩，總知就怪。餡亦太少，屌佢老母個濕鳩廚師扣扣埋埋d料留番俾佢老母做宵夜? 正一食屎狗。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣可以讚既，就係店員幾好禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n成餐咁就47蚊，好似食左一堆垃圾落肚，好唔撚抵，咁都做到開撚到分店，港豬真係食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7e18cf60a91ebe2f0d9203f23ee941ce548234","tid":220304,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bd4118d1fa660b98ece003218cb328aef58ce32","tid":220304,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">屌佢老母個濕鳩廚師扣扣埋埋d料留番俾佢老母做宵夜? 正一食屎狗。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6021ec5e4580b89b887dced2f58404cb922541","tid":220304,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:07:13.000Z","msg":"石硤尾有間粥舖好正"},{"pid":"6f2e9f855726c4129b9787b98863cab4dfe8bfa3","tid":220304,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">屌佢老母個濕鳩廚師扣扣埋埋d料留番俾佢老母做宵夜? 正一食屎狗。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e04b6909d4c4109733021b5d21d3e8d428ef1f9","tid":220304,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>石硤尾有間粥舖好正</blockquote><br />\n邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73bdf40a54e65383f64c9bc70f21d3654f35943","tid":220304,"uid":50202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:10:07.000Z","msg":"巴打講返正名大家會更清楚係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215f2ecdd7da80e79cfa5bbfeec849d1c6ca574b","tid":220304,"uid":50202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:10:26.000Z","msg":"係咪呻記？"},{"pid":"a67e6dc9facd0e18e28f0d25fe2a89e578614d18","tid":220304,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打講返正名大家會更清楚係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西記"},{"pid":"4c5583dc6878345ed57e34e289a7a4d8cdc5c4be","tid":220304,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪呻記？</blockquote><br />\n西記"},{"pid":"6b85e9dabda92b8a8303b4f9149d43103739fa98","tid":220304,"uid":73942,"like":0,"dislike"